https://coderwhodreams.com/blog/create-basic-login-forms-using-react-js-hooks-and-bootstrap/

Running the demo:

0) Launch backend server (available @ https://github.com/jcaporossi/auth-server):
    node index.js
1) Launch a private blockchain with ganache-cli: 
    ganache-cli
2) Compile smart contracts:
    truffle compile
3) Deploy smart contracts:
    truffle migrate
4) Launch application:
    cd client/
    yarn start
5) Use Chrome and install CORS enabling extension (and activate it !)   
